ASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6930832107044399", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8690568401070752"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "405798591820267"}]}, "change_log": "- Added a new pen called \"Cube.\"\n- Added a menu option to hide the hand outline when in MR mode.\n- Improved the stability of the palette position and orientation when hand tracking becomes unstable due to the overlap of the other hand with the hand opening the palette.\n- Improved the accuracy of pinch gesture recognition.\n- Fixed a bug where an invalid particle group was displayed at specific coordinates.", "created_date": 1729519191, "id": "8307357949391801", "version": "2.40", "version_code": 10, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6930832107044399", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8690568401070752"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "405798591820267"}]}, "change_log": "- Added support for Italian, Polish, and Dutch languages.\n- Enabled zooming in and out of images using pinch gestures with both middle fingers.\n- Improved recognition accuracy of pinch gestures and made it less likely for the orientation to shift upon completion.\n- Added a check in the tutorial to c